parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to the malfunction or non-deployment of airbags in the event of an accident, increasing the risk of injury or death to occupants.
symptoms: The airbag warning light illuminates on the dashboard
the passenger airbag sensor malfunctions
the airbag warning light turns on and off intermittently
the airbag system fails to deploy in an accident
and the dashboard cracks near the airbag housing.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the passenger airbag sensor can cause the airbag system to malfunction, leading to the non-deployment of airbags in the event of an accident, increasing the risk of injury or death to occupants.
symptoms: The passenger airbag warning light illuminates on the dashboard
the passenger airbag sensor malfunctions
the airbag warning light turns on and off intermittently
and the airbag system fails to deploy in an accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The cracking of the dashboard near the airbag housing can compromise the structural integrity of the airbag system, leading to the malfunction or non-deployment of airbags in the event of an accident, increasing the risk of injury or death to occupants.
symptoms: The dashboard cracks near the airbag housing
and the airbag system fails to deploy in an accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the timing chain can cause the engine to seize, leading to loss of power, stalling, and potentially causing accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The check engine light illuminates
the engine loses power
the vehicle stalls or hesitates
the engine makes a strange noise
the vehicle has reduced performance
the engine has a rough idle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine overheating can cause the engine to seize, leading to loss of power, stalling, and potentially causing accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The temperature gauge rises
the engine overheats
the vehicle loses power
the engine makes a strange noise
the vehicle has reduced performance.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition system can cause the vehicle to stall or not start, leading to safety risks and inconvenience.
symptoms: The key becomes stuck in the ignition
the ignition switch fails to turn
the vehicle stalls or fails to start
and the battery drains.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause various safety risks, including loss of power, airbag malfunctions, and electrical fires.

the airbag warning light illuminates

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can cause serious injury or death in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The airbag warning light illuminates

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the powertrain can cause loss of vehicle control, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle loses power
the engine stalls

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat and trim components can cause discomfort, distraction, and safety risks.
